critter.name: Great White Shark
critter.desc: Great white sharks are obviously known first and foremost for their biting. They are masters of the craft! They do lose teeth regularly through biting-related activities, but, luckily, those teeth grow back quickly. In fact, their missing teeth can be regrown in a single day. Just imagine their tooth-fairy-related income!
critter.quote: I caught a great white shark! Watch out for its jaws!
